'''Guillermo Martínez Ayala''' (born 15 March 1995), commonly known as "'''Memote'''",<ref>{{MedioTiempo|guillermo-martinez-ayala}}</ref> is a Mexican professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Forward (association football)|forward]] for [[Liga MX]] club [[Pumas UNAM|UNAM]] and the [[Mexico national football team|Mexico national team]].<ref>[http://chivaspasion.com/43608/zendejas-contreras-y-martinez-a-prestamo-zacatepec-mineros-mercado-junio-2017 Zendejas, Martínez y Contreras al Ascenso]‚ chivaspasion.com, 8 June 2017</ref>

==International career==
Martínez made his debut for the [[Mexico national football team|senior national team]] on 16 December 2023, in a friendly match against [[Colombia national football team|Colombia]] and scored a goal in a 2–3 defeat.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=ESPN|url=https://www.espn.com/soccer/match/_/gameId/688316/colombia-mexico|title=Mexico v Colombia game report|date=16 December 2023}}</ref>

